%F A029322 a(n) = floor((n+20)*(2*n^2+59*n-142)/35640 + ((2*n^2+1) mod 3)*(n+8)/27 + ((n+2) mod 3)*17/81 + ([(n mod 9)=4] - [(n mod 9)=8])/3 + ((7*n^3+3*n+4) mod 11)/11). - _Hoang Xuan Thanh_, Apr 15 2026
